# API origin only (no trailing slash, no /api suffix).
# Leave empty for same-origin API calls (recommended for Vercel production).
#
# Local development: leave empty — Vite dev server proxies /api to the backend.
#
# Production (Vercel): https://htd-roll-book.vercel.app
#   - Do NOT set VITE_API_BASE_URL in Vercel Environment Variables.
#   - vercel.json rewrites /api/* → http://187.77.99.225:8599/api/* (same-origin).
#   - Do NOT use Cloudflare for the Vercel hostname (*.vercel.app is managed by Vercel).
#   - Custom domain (e.g. htdrollbook.com) is optional later; see docs/VERCEL-SETUP.md.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
